The evidence with the title 'Tom Perez - Wikipedia ' says Thomas Edward Perez (born october 7, 1961) is an American Democratic Party politician and attorney who was elected chair of the Democratic National Committee in february 2017 . Perez was the United States secretary of labor from 2013 to 2017 . Prior to that he worked as a consumer advocate and civil rights attorney  ... He worked as aspecial counselor for senator Ted Kennedy until 1998  ... 
